@startuml SD_03_RSVP

title Scenario 3 — RSVP / Join Event Flow

skinparam defaultFontName  Arial
skinparam defaultFontSize  18

skinparam sequence {
  ArrowColor                  #374151
  ArrowFontSize               17
  ArrowFontStyle              bold
  ActorBorderColor            #2E7D32
  ActorBackgroundColor        #E8F5E9
  ActorFontSize               19
  ActorFontStyle              bold
  LifeLineBorderColor         #9CA3AF
  LifeLineBackgroundColor     #F3F4F6
  ParticipantBorderColor      #4A6CF7
  ParticipantBackgroundColor  #EEF2FF
  ParticipantFontSize         18
  ParticipantFontStyle        bold
  NoteBackgroundColor         #FEF9C3
  NoteBorderColor             #F59E0B
  NoteFontSize                16
  GroupBorderColor            #9CA3AF
  GroupBackgroundColor        #F3F4F6
  ActivationBorderColor       #4A6CF7
  ActivationBackgroundColor   #C7D2FE
}
skinparam ResponseMessageBelowArrow true

actor      "User"              as User
boundary   "HomeScreen"        as Home
boundary   "EventDetailScreen" as EDS
control    "EventService"      as EventSvc
control    "Backend API"       as API
entity     "MongoDB"           as DB

User       ->  Home        ++ : tap event card
Home       ->  EDS         ++ : onEventPress(eventId)
EDS        ->  EventSvc    ++ : getEventById(eventId)
EventSvc   ->  API         ++ : GET /api/events/:id
API        ->  DB          ++ : find event by id
DB        -->  API         -- : Event document
API       -->  EventSvc    -- : Event object
EventSvc  -->  EDS            : Event
deactivate EventSvc
EDS       -->  Home        -- : (render)
deactivate Home
EDS       -->  User           : render event detail

User       ->  EDS            : tap "Join"
EDS        ->  EventSvc    ++ : rsvpToEvent(eventId)
EventSvc   ->  API         ++ : POST /api/events/:id/rsvp
API        ->  DB          ++ : check filled vs capacity

alt Spots available
  DB       -->  API        -- : increment filled, add userId
  API      -->  EventSvc   -- : 200 OK
  EventSvc -->  EDS        -- : success
  EDS      ->   EDS           : setIsJoined(true)
  EDS      -->  User          : Alert "You're going to this event!"

else Event is full
  DB       -->  API        -- : add userId to waitlist
  API      -->  EventSvc   -- : 200 OK (waitlisted)
  EventSvc --> EDS         -- : waitlisted
  EDS      ->   EDS           : setIsJoined(true)
  EDS      -->  User          : Alert "Added to the waitlist"
end

deactivate EDS

@enduml
